---
const fronts = [
  ['01', 'Devocional Maná', '5 audios cada semana y agenda devocional para alimentar la fe en casa.'],
  ['02', 'Escuela Bíblica', '5 cursos discipulares para formar creyentes maduros y servidores.'],
  ['03', 'Iglesias Maná', 'Comunidades locales, misiones y grupos pequeños que impactan su entorno.'],
];

const objectives = [
  'Llevar el evangelio hasta lo último de la tierra.',
  'Discipular a quienes han nacido de nuevo hasta la madurez.',
  'Capacitar a los hijos de Dios en el uso de sus dones.',
];

const values = [
  'Palabra como fundamento',
  'Hábitos de vida piadosos',
  'Servicio y liderazgo',
  'Proclamación de la fe',
  'Adoración y consagración',
];

const programs = [
  ['Lunes 7:00 p.m.', 'Varones'],
  ['Lunes 7:30 p.m.', 'Cristianos Emprendedores'],
  ['Lunes 8:00 p.m.', 'Hablando con Dios'],
  ['Miércoles 7:00 p.m.', 'Mujeres'],
  ['Viernes 7:00 p.m.', 'Parejas'],
  ['Domingo 10:30 a.m.', 'Maná Familiar'],
];

const metrics = [
  ['14.600', 'Suscriptores en YouTube'],
  ['1.141', 'Videos publicados'],
  ['7.204', 'Seguidores en Facebook'],
  ['2.567', 'Seguidores en SoundCloud'],
];

const cities = [
  ['Medellín', 42, 27],
  ['Rionegro', 53, 32],
  ['Marinilla', 49, 40],
  ['Armenia', 35, 50],
  ['Ibagué', 48, 56],
  ['Bogotá', 58, 66],
  ['Cali', 28, 70],
  ['Quito', 78, 58],
  ['Cuenca', 82, 72],
];

const cspNonce = Astro.locals?.cspNonce;
---

<section class="mana-story-code" aria-label="Borrador del nuevo home de Ministerio Maná">
  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--hero" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--dark">
      <div class="mana-slide__art" data-mana-visual aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="mana-outline">ORAR</span>
        <span class="mana-script-ghost">Es momento de</span>
        <span class="mana-solid-ghost">AGRADECER</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-hero-grid">
        <div class="mana-copy-stack">
          <p class="mana-eyebrow" data-mana-split>Ministerio Maná</p>
          <h1 class="mana-hero-title">
            <span data-mana-split>Es momento de</span>
            <strong data-mana-title data-mana-split>ORAR</strong>
            <strong data-mana-title data-mana-split>AGRADECER</strong>
          </h1>
          <p class="mana-lead" data-mana-copy data-mana-split>
            Una iglesia que enseña las Escrituras, edifica vidas y forma discípulos para impactar su entorno cercano y el mundo.
          </p>
          <nav class="mana-actions" data-mana-ui aria-label="Acciones del borrador">
            <button type="button" class="mana-btn mana-btn--fill" data-mana-next>Comenzar historia</button>
            <a href="/eventos/cumbre-mundial-2026/" class="mana-btn mana-btn--line">Volver a Cumbre</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--mission" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--light">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-two-col">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Nuestra</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>MISIÓN</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-text-panel" data-mana-copy>
          <div class="mana-halo-logo" data-mana-visual aria-hidden="true">
            <span></span>
            <img src="/logo.svg" alt="" />
          </div>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Somos una iglesia que enseña las Escrituras, edificando las vidas de los hijos de Dios a través de hábitos espirituales que los lleven a conocer, amar y obedecer a Dios.
          </p>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Formamos hombres y mujeres guiados por el Espíritu Santo para establecer grupos pequeños e iglesias locales que impacten su entorno y el mundo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--vision" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--dark">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-vision-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Nuestra</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>VISIÓN</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-big-number" data-mana-visual data-mana-split>2030</div>
        <div class="mana-text-panel mana-text-panel--dark" data-mana-copy>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Ser una iglesia bíblica, cristocéntrica y relevante, con presencia nacional e internacional en el 2030.
          </p>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Una iglesia que discipula a quienes han nacido de nuevo y predica el evangelio como estilo de vida a través de todos los medios posibles.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--history" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--light">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-history-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Nuestra</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>HISTORIA</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-route" data-mana-visual>
          <span data-mana-split>Londres</span>
          <i></i>
          <strong data-mana-split>2016</strong>
          <i></i>
          <span data-mana-split>Medellín</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-text-panel" data-mana-copy>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Ministerio Maná surge tras la llegada a Medellín de los pastores Carlos Ríos y Gloria Cano desde Londres.
          </p>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Diez años antes, el Devocional Maná nació como podcast para llegar a creyentes en lugares apartados.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--fronts" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--dark">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-list-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>3 grandes</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>FRENTES</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-card-list" data-mana-stagger>
          {fronts.map(([number, title, detail]) => (
            <article>
              <span>{number}</span>
              <h3 data-mana-split>{title}</h3>
              <p>{detail}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--objectives" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--light">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-list-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Nuestros</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>OBJETIVOS</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-number-list" data-mana-stagger>
          {objectives.map((objective, index) => (
            <article>
              <span>{index + 1}</span>
              <p>{objective}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--values" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--dark">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-list-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Principios y</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>VALORES</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-value-grid" data-mana-stagger>
          {values.map((value) => <p>{value}</p>)}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--food" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--light">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-food-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Alimento</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>ESPIRITUAL</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-pill-cloud" data-mana-stagger>
          <span>21 Hábitos que Sanan</span>
          <span>Mi Casa</span>
          <span>Dos para Ser Uno</span>
          <span>Nacidos para Multiplicarnos</span>
          <span>Escogidos para Servir</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--churches" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--light">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-church-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Nuestras</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>IGLESIAS</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-code-map" data-mana-visual aria-hidden="true">
          <strong>Colombia</strong>
          <b>Ecuador</b>
          {cities.map(([city, x, y]) => <i style={`left:${x}%;top:${y}%`}>{city}</i>)}
        </div>
        <div class="mana-text-panel" data-mana-copy>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Presencia en 7 departamentos y 13 municipios, y en Ecuador en Cuenca y Quito.
          </p>
          <p data-mana-split>
            Iglesias y misiones dirigidas por líderes servidores bivocacionales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--virtual" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--dark">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-list-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Programas</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>VIRTUALES</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-schedule" data-mana-stagger>
          {programs.map(([time, name]) => (
            <article>
              <span>{time}</span>
              <strong>{name}</strong>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--impact" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--light">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-impact-grid">
        <div class="mana-title-lockup">
          <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Nuestro</p>
          <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>IMPACTO</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mana-metrics" data-mana-stagger>
          {metrics.map(([value, label]) => (
            <article>
              <strong>{value}</strong>
              <span>{label}</span>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="mana-country-strip" data-mana-visual>
          <span>Colombia 1,2M</span>
          <span>Estados Unidos 1,07M</span>
          <span>Ecuador 90K</span>
          <span>España 66K</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mana-scene mana-scene--final" data-mana-scene>
    <div class="mana-slide mana-slide--dark">
      <div class="mana-slide__content mana-final-grid">
        <p class="mana-script" data-mana-split>Ministerio Maná</p>
        <h2 data-mana-title data-mana-split>Conocer, amar, obedecer y servir.</h2>
        <p data-mana-copy data-mana-split>
          Este borrador vive separado del home actual para seguir refinándolo hasta que esté listo para reemplazarlo.
        </p>
        <nav class="mana-actions" data-mana-ui aria-label="Acciones finales">
          <a href="/devocional/" class="mana-btn mana-btn--fill">Devocional Maná</a>
          <a href="/iglesias/" class="mana-btn mana-btn--line">Encontrar iglesia</a>
          <a href="/" class="mana-btn mana-btn--line">Home actual</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="mana-slide-progress" aria-hidden="true"><span data-mana-progress></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>

<style>
  @font-face {
    font-family: "Mana Script";
    src: url("/fonts/SUMMER%20FONT/Summer%20Loving%20Regular.otf") format("opentype");
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: normal;
    font-display: swap;
  }

  :global(html) {
    scroll-behavior: auto;
  }

  :global(html),
  :global(body) {
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .mana-story-code {
    --navy: #293c74;
    --deep: #111b42;
    --ink: #17245b;
    --teal: #28a6bd;
    --sky: #cbd9e6;
    --beige: #f5efeb;
    --white: #fff;
    --header-offset: var(--mana-header-offset, 72px);
    --slide-h: calc(100svh - var(--header-offset));
    background: var(--deep);
    color: var(--ink);
    isolation: isolate;
    overflow-x: clip;
  }

  @supports (height: 100dvh) {
    .mana-story-code {
      --slide-h: calc(100dvh - var(--header-offset));
    }
  }

  .mana-story-code,
  .mana-story-code * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .mana-scene {
    min-height: var(--slide-h);
    height: var(--slide-h);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .mana-slide {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: var(--slide-h);
    min-height: var(--slide-h);
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: clamp(22px, 5vw, 72px);
    transform-origin: center center;
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  .mana-slide--dark {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 84% 12%, rgba(40, 166, 189, 0.24), transparent 22%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 92%, rgba(40, 166, 189, 0.16), transparent 24%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #22366f 0%, #293c74 46%, #17245b 100%);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .mana-slide--light {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 8%, rgba(203, 217, 230, 0.8), transparent 22%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 8% 94%, rgba(40, 166, 189, 0.14), transparent 26%),
      var(--beige);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .mana-slide::before,
  .mana-slide::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .mana-slide::before {
    top: -94px;
    right: -42px;
    width: clamp(130px, 20vw, 280px);
    height: clamp(130px, 20vw, 280px);
    border-radius: 0 0 0 58%;
    background: var(--teal);
  }

  .mana-slide::after {
    left: -74px;
    bottom: -86px;
    width: clamp(130px, 20vw, 260px);
    height: clamp(130px, 20vw, 260px);
    border: 2px solid rgba(40, 166, 189, 0.42);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .mana-slide__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, 100%);
    max-height: calc(var(--slide-h) - clamp(44px, 10vw, 144px));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .mana-slide__art {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .mana-outline,
  .mana-script-ghost,
  .mana-solid-ghost {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0.28;
  }

  .mana-outline {
    left: 31%;
    top: 25%;
    color: transparent;
    font-family: "Intro", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(5.5rem, 15vw, 13rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.8;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 4px var(--teal);
    text-stroke: 4px var(--teal);
  }

  .mana-script-ghost {
    left: 44%;
    top: 43%;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: "Mana Script", cursive;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 6.8rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .mana-solid-ghost {
    left: 52%;
    top: 54%;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: "Intro", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .mana-hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: min(620px, 100%);
  }

  .mana-copy-stack {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .mana-eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    font-size: clamp(0.94rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .mana-hero-title {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: "Mana Script", cursive;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 4.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .mana-hero-title > span,
  .mana-script {
    display: block;
    font-family: "Mana Script", cursive;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .mana-hero-title strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-family: "Intro", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 9vw, 7.6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.84;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .mana-lead,
  .mana-text-panel p,
  .mana-final-grid > p:not(.mana-script) {
    margin: 0;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: clamp(0.98rem, 1.55vw, 1.22rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .mana-lead {
    max-width: 670px;
    margin-top: clamp(18px, 3vw, 30px);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
  }

  .mana-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
  }

  .mana-btn {
    border: 0;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 13px 18px;
    font-family: "Intro", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .mana-btn--fill {
    background: var(--teal);
    color: var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 52px rgba(40, 166, 189, 0.22);
  }

  .mana-btn--line {
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    background: transparent;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .mana-two-col,
  .mana-list-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 0.78fr) minmax(0, 1.22fr);
    gap: clamp(26px, 5vw, 66px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mana-title-lockup {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .mana-script {
    margin: 0 0 2px;
    color: currentColor;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.1rem);
    line-height: 0.82;
  }

  .mana-title-lockup h2,
  .mana-food-grid h2,
  .mana-final-grid h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-family: "Intro", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 10vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.82;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .mana-text-panel {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(12px, 2vw, 22px);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--teal);
    padding: clamp(14px, 3vw, 28px) 0 clamp(14px, 3vw, 28px) clamp(18px, 3vw, 38px);
    color: rgba(23, 36, 91, 0.86);
  }

  .mana-text-panel--dark {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
  }

  .mana-halo-logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: clamp(-118px, -11vw, -84px);
    left: clamp(18px, 3vw, 38px);
    width: clamp(78px, 10vw, 126px);
    height: clamp(78px, 10vw, 126px);
    border: 3px solid var(--teal);
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .mana-halo-logo span {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 100%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 2px;
    height: 72px;
    background: var(--teal);
  }

  .mana-halo-logo img {
    width: 45%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .mana-vision-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.64fr 0.56fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: clamp(22px, 4vw, 52px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mana-vision-grid .mana-text-panel {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    max-width: 960px;
  }

  .mana-big-number {
    justify-self: end;
    color: rgba(40, 166, 189, 0.24);
    font-family: "Intro", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(5.4rem, 16vw, 14rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.76;
  }

  .mana-history-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(240px, 0.7fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: clamp(18px, 4vw, 52px);
    align-items: center;
